{"tid":2365938,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡頓堡：不要再做偽君子了高普，利物浦的人也假摔","createTime":"2021-01-14T06:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T10:50:30.000Z","uid":38189,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"de127fa2171cc7cd21f3f8c36d815dad8f8c7726","tid":2365938,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"英超著名裁判卡頓堡今天在自己的每日郵報專欄裡朝利物浦主帥高普直接開砲，他表示高普收起他偽君子的那套說辭吧，利物浦的球員也假摔。 而克洛普的這種針對曼聯的行為向裁判施壓的做法還是從費格遜爵士的戰術手冊中學來的呢，他認為利物浦主帥現在應該更加擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n卡頓堡表示，高普上一場賽後針對主帥保羅-蒂爾尼的評論完全是從費格遜爵士的戰術手冊中學來的，而他的目的就是為了影響裁判，並且在雙紅會之前讓這種想法深深植入蒂爾尼的大腦。"},{"pid":"5d2db7e32c825cafc3b2afadc0f04aef4570978d","tid":2365938,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffac8fcd23ca8632ac6cc72da0f54c63237b4d3","tid":2365938,"uid":33770,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"從費格遜爵士的戰術手冊中學來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74fea8954568a470b66cd5454c493f447a234fb","tid":2365938,"uid":33770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/babuyagu/status/1348979101902778369?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbabuyagu%2Fstatus%2F1348979101902778369%3Fs%3D21&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuProWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=cb6bc25b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbabuyagu%2Fstatus%2F1348979101902778369%3Fs%3D21&h=ffcfee20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/babuyagu/status/1348979101902778369?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"f2fa6a818a7322b264a7ea43db11f7f9bc12323d","tid":2365938,"uid":172627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ffa